ock Essential 有两种不同的版本：一种带有 Google Assistant，另一种则由<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9MZW5vdm8tU21hcnQtQ2xvY2stRXNzZW50aWFsLUJ1aWx0L2RwL0IwOUxSSldDUEI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8teTEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImJjM2I5ZjQ4LWRmZTItMzZiYi05YWViLWQzMWFiZWI5ZjZlNyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfJ1qMEijpyTBtOd0T9DXTcHwtgB07kwJcWmKX-CNfbd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLenovo-Smart-Clock-Essential-Built%2Fdp%2FB09LRJWCPB">Alexa 提供支持</a>。带有 Google Assistant 的产品有一个内置夜灯、一个用于为设备充电的额外 USB 端口和一个麦克风静音按钮。另一方面，带有 Alexa 的扩展坞与可选的扩展坞兼容，该扩展坞可与无线充电板或环境光扩展坞（它有海狮或鱿鱼形状）等配件一起使用。作为夜灯。</p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-display-202448797.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-display-202448797.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> bc3b9f48-dfe2-36bb-9aeb-d31abeb9f6e7</guid><dc:creator>妮可·李</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 14:00:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687788021</ingested><modified> 2023-06-26T14:00:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[amazon]]></category><category><![CDATA[BuyersGuide]]></category><category><![CDATA[smarthome2020]]></category><category><![CDATA[thebuyersguide]]></category><category><![CDATA[google]]></category><category><![CDATA[commerce]]></category><category><![CDATA[lenovo]]></category><category><![CDATA[gear]]></category><category><![CDATA[home]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicEquipment,Instruments&Components]]></category><category><![CDATA[Home&Garden]]></catego